description: [``botocore``] AWS CodeBuild now adds additional compute types for reserved capacity fleet.
[``botocore``] GuardDuty RDS Protection expands support for Amazon Aurora PostgreSQL Limitless Databases.
[``botocore``] API changes for new named tag expressions feature.
[``botocore``] Introduces category apis in AmazonQApps. Web experience users use Categories to tag and filter library items.
[``botocore``] Fix ListStorageLensConfigurations and ListStorageLensGroups deserialization for Smithy SDKs.
[``botocore``] Adding BatchGetPolicy API which supports the retrieval of multiple policies across multiple policy stores within a single request.
[``botocore``] Added support for header enabling service migration off the AWS Query protocol.
